reviewText: This DVD arrived on time and in good condition.  Robert Mitchum is one of my all time favourite Movie Stars and he does not disappoint in this one.  Good Story and lots of "Mitchum Action".
Mr. Mitchum, a brilliant actor, bombed in this one which is not worth watching.
I love this film. Has a lot of good action and suspense in it.

Robert Mitchum did quite a few of these pics, in these one it's a War Thriller and he's an American journalist who picks up a gun.

Not a bad find.  I liked it.
